summary: Force people across rooms into walls or flattened entire armies in seconds
descriptionHtml:
[heading][font=verdana]DESCRIPTION[/heading]
Force people across rooms into walls or flattened entire armies in seconds
This spell is the inverse of telekinesis, it will push away whatever you aim at
Very fun to have this in one hand and send them flying, and then blast them with flames with the other :D
You can also use it to quickly mess up someones house really bad

[heading]INSTALLATION[/heading]
Unpack .rar contents to Data\\
Open console ingame and type: help \"telekinetic\"
It will come up with something like (22000D64) \"Telekinetic Push\"
Then type: player.addspell 22000D64
